## FAQ

**How do I reset my password?**
Tap "Forgot Password" on the login screen and follow the instructions sent to your email.

**How do I cancel my subscription?**
Subscriptions are managed through your Apple ID. Go to Settings → Apple ID → Subscriptions → CalmNest → Cancel.

**The app is crashing. What should I do?**
Try closing and reopening the app. If the issue persists, update to the latest version or contact us.

**How do I delete my account?**
Email us at the address above and we'll process your request within 48 hours.

